Help us improve this site

   This is the beta version of "inside NTNU", the English language innsida, NTNU's Norwegian intranet. A new intranet is in the works, but in the meantime we've made these stopgap pages to help
   non-Norwegian speakers. How can we make it better? Let us know what you think.
