Get the latest news from NIRS via email

   Want to keep up-to-date on news from NTNU's International Researcher Support group? All you have to do is to send an email to sympa@admin.ntnu.no with "Subscribe nirs-news" in the subject line
   (and nothing else in the email). You can also subscribe to the "NTNU International Researcher Support" message channel on Innsida, where you can also find a complete description of how to
   subscribe to a message channel.

   previous updates

Need more help?

   If you don't find the information that you need on these webpages, first contact your faculty or department adviser to see if he or she can help.

   Your next step is to contact International Researcher Support for more help or advice.

